- This contains sample roles/policies for AWS
- The pc-global-security-boundary is a boundary policy to be attached to each role
- No role can exist without boundary
- The role pcsecurity-crossaccount-operator in the dir and all other roles must have the boundary attached to it
- This pcsecurity-crossaccount-operator-trust-relationships contains all users who can assume this role
- This is the sample structure for cross account access as a Ops guy
